 done."],[2097,2227,"You bastard!"],[2227,2344,"I'll fucking kill you!"],[2348,2423,"Luke, stop!"],[2786,2857,"Did you just"],[2857,2969,"push me?"],[3086,3153,"What the hell is"],[3153,3203,"wrong with you?"],[3203,3365,"That's my brother!"],[3365,3445,"Do you know"],[3445,3561,"who he is?"],[3561,3657,"His company just"],[3657,3712,"signed a deal with"],[3712,3762,"the richest"],[3762,3791,"guy in the"],[3791,3878,"whole damn state!"],[3908,3999,"I'm calling the cops!"],[3999,4091,"Go ahead, Amy."],[4091,4175,"Call the cops."],[4175,4291,"Let's see what happens."],[4291,4421,"You bitch!"],[4421,4462,"I'll show you"],[4462,4500,"what happens"],[4500,4533,"when you mess"],[4533,4608,"with a Bennett."],[5059,5188,"You pushed me"],[5188,5305,"for him?"],[5392,5472,"I'm your"],[5472,5659,"husband, Alyssa!"],[5659,5751,"Touch him again,"],[5751,5814,"and I won't"],[5814,5980,"stop at a push."],[5980,6081,"Next time, it'll be"],[6081,6185,"divorce papers."]],"15":[[50,246,"She's leaving me..."],[246,442,"for another man?"],[521,588,"Alyssa,"],[588,679,"don't push me."],[721,971,"Come home now or never come back."],[1071,1172,"You'll lose everything."],[1172,1359,"The money, the title."],[1459,1539,"Everything."],[1539,1651,"No, Luke."],[1739,1822,"You're the one who's"],[1822,1951,"going to lose everything."],[2064,2260,"Sorry for the interruption, ma'am."],[2260,2444,"Here's the bill for your stay."],[2444,2552,"Let me know if everything's alright,"],[2552,2698,"and we will process your payment."],[2977,3157,"Sorry, I've got to take this."],[3157,3253,"Work call."],[3253,3340,"Don't worry."],[3340,3465,"Nate'll be here soon."],[3465,3607,"It's okay."],[3607,3753,"They can't touch me."],[4387,4500,"Would you look at that?"],[4500,4600,"Your knight in shining armor"],[4600,4825,"ran off with the first mention of money."],[4825,4929,"Alyssa,"],[4929,5055,"you really know how to pick them?"],[5055,5313,"Yeah. I fell for your brother after all."],[5392,5509,"That was three years ago."],[5509,5789,"I'm older and wiser now."],[5789,5926,"Men like him,"],[5926,6110,"they need to stay at the bottom"],[6110,6202,"where they belong."],[6202,6281,"You bitch!"],[6627,6781,"I'll pay."],[6781,6923,"How much?"],[6923,7102,"That would be three million dollars, sir."],[7178,7344,"Three million dollars?"]],"16":[[33,120,"Three million."],[166,387,"That's half of your profit this year,"],[387,563,"isn't it, Mr. Bennett?"],[617,746,"You still want to cover the bill?"],[896,1013,"Fine."],[1013,1084,"I'll pay."],[1159,1317,"But you have to come home"],[1317,1405,"with me."],[1472,1543,"Hold on."],[1543,1651,"She cheated on you,"],[1651,1793,"and you're still going to pay for her."],[1793,1901,"She wants a divorce."],[1901,2081,"Let her pay her own damn bill."],[2081,2198,"Isn't that what all strong,"],[2198,2318,"independent women do?"],[2552,2990,"Daddy! I've missed you so much."],[2990,3311,"I want you to stay with me forever."],[3386,3599,"Please, daddy?"],[3599,3816,"I am so sorry, Luke."],[3816,3928,"She woke up crying and"],[3928,4137,"just wouldn't stop asking for you."],[4154,4308,"Have your little family reunion"],[4308,4416,"somewhere else."],[4462,4592,"Nurse, they're disturbing me."],[4592,4725,"Please escort them out."],[4750,4875,"You can't even pay your own bill"],[4875,5013,"and you want us kicked out?"],[5013,5125,"Please."],[5125,5230,"People like you don't belong"],[5230,5392,"in VIP rooms anyway."],[5455,5714,"Three million is nothing to me."],[5714,5860,"And just so you know,"],[5860,5951,"around here,"],[5951,6076,"my word carries more weight"],[6076,6164,"than my wallet."]],"17":[[37,108,"Alyssa,"],[108,233,"do you have a case of postpartum"],[233,392,"delusion or something?"],[392,467,"Your last name might"],[467,575,"happen to be Davenport,"],[625,746,"but you're an orphan."],[779,875,"It's not like you're part of the"],[875,1046,"Davenports who own this hospital."],[1142,1259,"And what if I am?"],[1330,1459,"What would you do then?"],[1459,1526,"Nurse,"],[1526,1605,"do you know her?"],[1605,1826,"Is she someone important here?"],[1826,2035,"Sorry, ma'am."],[2035,2173,"I'm new."],[2173,2331,"I'm not sure."],[2331,2477,"See, the nurse just says"],[2477,2627,"she doesn't know who you are."],[2644,2769,"You're nobody."],[2815,2948,"Go get whoever's in charge."],[2948,3144,"I want to teach this lying bitch a lesson."],[3182,3319,"Amy, the president of"],[3319,3407,"Saint Mary's Hospital"],[3407,3532,"is a very busy man."],[3599,3691,"What if he gets upset"],[3691,3749,"and kicks us out"],[3749,3953,"before Lilly can see Dr. Davenport?"],[3978,4087,"Do you hear that?"],[4087,4258,"If Lilly misses her appointment,"],[4258,4350,"it's all on you!"],[4391,4521,"If that happens,"],[4521,4658,"we'll bury you in lawsuits"],[4658,4742,"and make sure you rot"],[4742,4913,"in prison for the rest of your life!"],[4913,5163,"God, will you stop screaming at me?"],[5163,5267,"You're giving me a headache."],[5476,5643,"I am warning you, Amy Bennett."],[5643,5855,"Touch me again, and I will be sure"],[5855,5985,"to make you regret it."],[6135,6260,"What the hell is going on?"],[6343,6544,"President Davenport, sir,"],[6544,6806,"I'm so sorry for the for the disturbance."],[6806,6881,"Um..."],[6931,6994,"It's just my..."],[6994,7061,"my wife"],[7061,7203,"somehow weaseled her way into the"],[7203,7361,"VIP room without my permission."],[7478,7603,"Actually, we were just going."],[7603,7665,"Alyssa,"],[7665,7728,"come on."],[7728,7895,"Don't touch me!"],[7953,8087,"You make my skin crawl."],[8087,8204,"God, you're the most shameless"],[8204,8333,"tramp I've ever met."],[8366,8475,"I wish you never married"],[8475,8579,"into our family."],[8579,8662,"All you've done is drag"],[8662,8779,"our name through the mud."],[8817,8900,"President Davenport,"],[8900,9054,"this psycho snuck her way into the VIP"],[9054,9288,"room and is refusing to pay."],[9321,9430,"I think you should throw her onto"],[9430,9559,"the street where she belongs."],[9763,9934,"I should be doing that to you!"]],"18":[[104,250,"President Davenport."],[250,325,"You're supposed to be in charge"],[325,425,"of this whole hospital."],[425,642,"She's the one trying to stay here for free."],[642,842,"Why are you coming after me?"],[842,955,"Of course she can stay here for free."],[955,1026,"I can't..."],[1026,1167,"I can't imagine why anyone would"],[1167,1326,"even charge her in the first place!"],[1426,1601,"Lucy, you should have known better."],[1601,1743,"That woman over there is one of our"],[1743,1881,"VIPs."],[1881,2027,"Anything she needs at this hospital,"],[2027,2181,"she gets for free!"],[2181,2293,"Don't charge her again!"],[2369,2527,"What?"],[2527,2619,"Alyssa, since when have you"],[2619,2802,"been the VIP of anything?"],[2857,3011,"You're not privy to that information"],[3011,3119,"because you're no longer"],[3119,3224,"welcome here."],[3269,3357,"And I know that"],[3357,3470,"you've been desperate"],[3470,3603,"to try to get to our"],[3603,3824,"cardiac surgeon, Dr. Davenport."],[3824,3974,"I'm going to tell you right now,"],[4058,4204,"Dr. Davenport's no longer going"],[4204,4329,"to be taking your patient."],[4408,4454,"Luke!"],[4454,4629,"What are we going to do with Lilly?"],[4629,4821,"We have to save her!"],[4871,4984,"Mr. Davenport, sir."],[4984,5230,"I'm sorry, my sister here. She's young."],[5230,5380,"She didn't mean what she said."],[5380,5480,"If you could just give her"],[5480,5668,"another chance to make things right."],[5693,5901,"She didn't mean it."],[5901,6089,"She didn't mean it like she didn't mean"],[6089,6185,"to hit me"],[6185,6352,"when she knew I was pregnant?"],[6352,6431,"Luke,"],[6431,6702,"you have always turned a blind eye"],[6702,6869,"to what they've been doing to me."],[6952,7148,"You've never fucking loved me!"],[7148,7357,"Well, what about you?"],[7357,7449,"When did you get together"],[7449,7603,"with that guy? Huh?"],[7603,7770,"Is Vivian even mine?"],[9142,9275,"Luke,"],[9275,9396,"I want a divorce."],[9559,9701,"We're done."]],"19":[[792,855,"What happened?"],[888,971,"They didn't hurt you again,"],[971,1051,"did they?"],[1163,1301,"Seems like she'll throw away"],[1301,1451,"everything we had."],[1509,1830,"Even our marriage, for that guy."],[1968,2168,"I need you to draft something for me."],[2318,2523,"I'm divorcing Luke."],[3061,3294,"Alyssa, are you sure?"],[3294,3445,"You've been a stay-at-home housewife"],[3445,3561,"for the past three years."],[3561,3757,"You've never even had a job."],[3782,3874,"I mean, who's,"],[3874,3962,"who's gonna look after"],[3962,4049,"you and Vivian?"],[4066,4149,"You think your little boy toy"],[4149,4204,"is going to do that?"],[4204,4362,"That is none of your business."],[4441,4587,"It's over, Luke."],[6189,6239,"Luke,"],[6239,6427,"you are not going to believe this."],[6427,6656,"Davenport Corp. just called."],[6656,6731,"They want to go with"],[6731,6798,"Bennett Businesses"],[6798,6961,"for their new real estate project."],[6998,7082,"This is Davenport."],[7082,7240,"Like, The Davenport Corp,"],[7240,7390,"one of the most prestigious"],[7390,7499,"corporations in the world."],[7545,7670,"The real estate moguls have been"],[7670,7795,"fighting tooth and nail for that project,"],[7795,7953,"and now it's ours!"],[7953,8083,"Once we complete this project,"],[8083,8208,"we will be the biggest"],[8208,8437,"real estate company in town!"],[8516,8696,"Too bad poor Alyssa is not going to get"],[8696,8821,"to enjoy any of it."],[8871,9017,"Oh, I'm sure she's regretting"],[9017,9171,"her decision right now."],[9171,9288,"It must feel awful"],[9288,9476,"having just divorced Luke."]],"20":[[0,196,"I threw him away."],[196,304,"You are free to dig"],[304,346,"him back"],[346,467,"out of the dumpster."],[467,538,"But do you really"],[538,617,"think that Davenport"],[617,654,"gave him the"],[654,729,"project based on his"],[729,800,"own merit?"],[884,950,"What are you"],[950,1017,"talking about,"],[1017,1092,"Alyssa?"],[1092,1197,"Of course he's the"],[1197,1280,"reason Davenport"],[1280,1326,"wants to work with"],[1326,1393,"us."],[1393,1443,"Who else could it"],[1443,1509,"be?"],[1509,1564,"You?"],[1634,1747,"What? Are you"],[1747,1780,"going to tell us"],[1780,1847,"you're a secret"],[1847,1922,"heiress now"],[1922,2006,"or something?"],[2006,2122,"And what if I am?"],[2168,2314,"As if!"],[2314,2373,"You're a"],[2373,2414,"broke,"],[2414,2477,"jobless,"],[2477,2535,"orphan!"],[2535,2569,"You don't even"],[2569,2615,"know what this"],[2615,2690,"project's about."],[2744,2831,"The Davenport"],[2831,2936,"project is our"],[2936,3040,"trump card."],[3040,3136,"They are bringing in"],[3136,3232,"top tier talent for"],[3232,3319,"this real estate"],[3319,3403,"project."],[3403,3516,"INSIDIA tech,"],[3516,3632,"Harvard Medicine"],[3632,3703,"are sending their"],[3703,3832,"best people here."],[3832,3912,"Once we have this"],[3912,3970,"project complete,"],[3970,4049,"we'll have no"],[4049,4112,"trouble finding"],[4112,4200,"a cure for Lilly."],[4300,4404,"So that's why Luke"],[4404,4454,"tried so hard"],[4454,4525,"to get on the"],[4525,4646,"project."],[4646,4750,"It's all because of"],[4750,4859,"you and Lilly."],[4934,5100,"What a noble man,"],[5100,5213,"putting your woman"],[5213,5397,"and daughter first."],[5397,5472,"Alyssa!"],[5472,5555,"For the love of God,"],[5555,5613,"stop throwing a"],[5613,5693,"tantrum and just"],[5693,5755,"come home with"],[5755,5809,"me!"]],"21":[[0,54,"Just come"],[54,91,"home with me!"],[91,145,"home with me!"],[162,216,"Home?"],[258,367,"I am going home."],[442,546,"To my real home."],[625,721,"About time, buttercup."],[775,779,"The cavalry's here."],[779,892,"The cavalry's here."],[2014,2114,"How?"],[2114,2189,"I didnt know Alyssa's"],[2189,2344,"side piece was that rich!"],[2544,2765,"It seems to me that Alyssa and"],[2765,2973,"this guy are pretty serious."],[2973,3203,"Well, I doubt he'd do that for just anyone."],[3499,3595,"Alyssa!"],[3745,3866,"You can divorce me,"],[3866,4033,"but you're not taking Vivian."],[4054,4204,"She's not growing up calling another"],[4204,4304,"man her father."],[4337,4458,"Come on, Alyssa."],[4458,4567,"You've just given birth,"],[4567,4667,"and you're already so"],[4667,4788,"desperate to leave."],[4854,4963,"I mean,"],[4963,5088,"I hate to say this,"],[5088,5342,"but who's really the cheater here, huh?"]],"22":[[25,120,"There's something going on between"],[120,283,"you two, isn't there?"],[283,483,"Why else would you leave with him?"],[483,729,"You don't deserve an answer."],[729,846,"You left me while I was"],[846,963,"dying in the hospital"],[963,1030,"so you could be"],[1030,1134,"with another woman."],[1263,1463,"You don't deserve to be Vivian's father."],[1463,1643,"She's my flesh and blood!"],[1643,1780,"I have a right to see her!"],[1780,1926,"Oh, you want rights?"],[1926,2110,"You'll have to see me in court."],[2331,2523,"I'll make you eat your words, Alyssa."],[2581,2731,"Don't make me do this."],[2752,2890,"Luke Bennett,"],[2957,3240,"my biggest regret in life is ever"],[3240,3319,"marrying you."],[3495,3578,"When I think"],[3578,3678,"about the three years that"],[3678,3807,"I wasted with you,"],[3807,3937,"every time,"],[3937,4149,"makes me sick to my stomach."],[4567,4583,"you..."],[4583,4679,"Alyssa,"],[4679,4979,"you really left me for another man?"],[5217,5351,"Don't be upset, Luke."],[5351,5538,"I'm sure Alyssa didn't mean it."],[5538,5680,"See? She's still wearing"],[5680,5764,"your wedding ring."],[5893,6035,"Thanks for the reminder."],[6122,6227,"Almost forgot,"],[6227,6389,"my last piece of trash."],[6489,6610,"Luke, three years ago,"],[6610,6769,"you saved my life."],[6769,6986,"And in return, I gave your company"],[6986,7228,"three years of growth."],[7228,7428,"From now on,"],[7428,7557,"I don't owe you anything."]],"23":[[246,316,"All right."],[316,383,"Roll out!"],[383,517,"I've given you too many"],[517,684,"second chances, Luke."],[717,838,"From now on,"],[838,946,"you're dead to me."],[984,1042,"Alyssa!"],[1096,1205,"Alyssa!"],[1710,1772,"Don't know how you can stand"],[1772,1843,"touching that thing,"],[1843,2018,"knowing whose fat hand it was just on."],[2018,2193,"That's my wife you're talking about."],[2193,2264,"What?"],[2293,2439,"You're divorced now."],[2439,2627,"You should be putting Krystal first,"],[2627,2698,"and Lilly."],[2698,2886,"She's already calling you daddy."],[2977,3123,"Once the project's finished,"],[3140,3324,"I'll explain everything to Alyssa"],[3324,3486,"and get her and Vivian back."],[3632,3778,"As for me and Krystal,"],[3841,3987,"its not what you think."],[4170,4258,"Please don't be upset with"],[4258,4366,"your brother, Amy."],[4366,4533,"I really don't mind."],[4567,4788,"Luke, I'm so sorry."],[4829,4942,"It's all my fault."],[4942,5088,"I made Alyssa mad."],[5150,5271,"I'll take the fall for this,"],[5271,5447,"and I'll explain everything for her."],[5447,5551,"I appreciate it,"],[5551,5705,"but it's not you, Krystal."],[5726,5880,"When my old boss passed,"],[5880,5976,"I promised him that"],[5976,6147,"I would take care of you and Lilly."],[6644,6798,"I'm a man of my word."],[6881,6981,"I have to make sure"],[6981,7119,"Alyssa never comes back."],[7119,7340,"If anyone's going to be Mrs. Bennett,"],[7340,7436,"it'll be me."]],"24":[[429,563,"Miss Jane,"],[563,696,"at your service."],[696,734,"at your service."],[2452,2581,"Like what I got you, munchkin?"],[2590,2794,"I don't need all this, Uncle Jason."],[2852,2940,"Come on, Jane,"],[2940,3023,"you're my niece."],[3065,3165,"Of course, me and Nate only want"],[3165,3232,"what's best for you."],[3274,3386,"You say jump,"],[3386,3511,"we ask how high?"],[3682,3770,"When is Uncle Nate"],[3770,3899,"coming back, by the way?"],[3953,4129,"Don't even get me started."],[4129,4241,"He was so happy when I told him"],[4241,4379,"you divorced Luke."],[4379,4504,"He's busy with Harvard Medical"],[4504,4558,"